Node.js is a JS freamework
Node.js is a JS freamework , open source , cross-platform , single threaded

featsurs :
            - JS
            - ES - Ecma Script
            - fast performance
            - support a lot of library
            - support async process
            - real time - chating - notification - request response ;
            - single thread

Node.js dependancies :
            -Js code standards : ECMA Script
            -Modules : Common JS
            -Js Engin : V8 Engin : ecexcute code in sync - single thread v8 call stack C++
            -Libuv : async handler (async) C - multithreaded
            -npm : manager dependacer manager tool : management tool for js